      • any

        @SafeVarargs
public static <T> Predicate<T> any(Predicate<? super T>... predicates)
        Returns a Predicate that evaluates to true if any of the given predicates evaluates to true. If predicates is empty, the returned Predicate will always evaluate to false.

      • all

        @SafeVarargs
public static <T> Predicate<T> all(Predicate<? super T>... predicates)
        Returns a Predicate that evaluates to true if all of the given conditions evaluates to true. If conditions is empty, the returned Condition will always evaluate to true.
